mport.\n- **Modify:** `worldcup_playoff/data/__init__.py` \u2014 export `resolve_r32`, `R32_SLOTS`, `rank_third_places`, `assign_thirds`; extend `__all__`.\n- Import only the `GroupStanding` type from `live.py` (one-way). Do **not** simulate, sample, or compute probabilities here \u2014 that is Cycle 5. Stop at producing `(home, away)` pairs from *given* standings.",
